      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It has been meticulously cared for, always kept in the garage, and looks stunning from every angle. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that feels and looks brand new, this is definitely the one for you. I've loved every mile in it, and I can't wait for it to go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
