    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement. The chassis is rock-solid with documented rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high-lateral loads. Performance is sharpened by the factory-spec limited-slip differential and a pristine suspension geometry. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the car retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback and high-revving linear power delivery. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
